A. V. Bramble https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A._V._Bramble 0 Albert Victor Bramble (1884–1963) was an English actor and film director. He began his acting career on the stage. He started acting in films in 1913, and subsequently turned to directing and producing films. He died on 17 May 1963. Albert_Victor_Bramble ( 1884 – 1963 ) was an_English_actor_and_film_director .
